# PowerPoint Templates for multiple screens

### Advice for using a 7-screen template
* If you are bringing in a remote participant via a third party application such as Google Hangouts, Skype or Zoom, this will take up screen real estate. We can duplicate remote participants onto an additional video-conference screen and then duplicate one of your content slides to take full advantage of all seven screens for your presentation. 
* For this reason, we highly encourage you to follow the advice in [Tips for organizing your presentation content](https://github.com/AK-NSF-EPSCoR/decision-theater-north/wiki/Design-your-Presentation-Content) and make the content on screens 1 and 7 exactly the same throughout your presentation. 
* This will allow us to duplicate the content without any loss

